MediaPlayerPanel
public class FlashAppletPanel
extends org.apache.wicket.markup.html.panel.Panel
implements org.apache.wicket.markup.html.IHeaderContributor

Component to render a Flash applet. You specify parameters such as width, height, whether full-screen access is desired, and pass in the Flash object. This uses JavaScriptFlashGateway after page load to actually insert the Flash portably. Not all possible Flashvars are currently supported by this class, for instance allowscriptaccess, and background color are not but may be added in the future.
